{"tid":2073412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐狗無好下場]【武漢肺炎】北京百事廠房 8 人確診　廠房停產、產品封存","createTime":"2020-06-21T10:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T11:36:23.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"570912489986034e0a423aae5f27e2c5b9ca2e5b","tid":2073412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\ntSpon5s mgsineoredausts &middot;<br />\n<br />\n近日北京再有超過 200 人確診武漢肺炎，外界關注是否有第二波疫情爆發。百事可樂公司今（21 日）證實，在北京大興廠房內有 8 宗確診病例，其中 2 人曾到過爆發多宗案例的新發地市場採購，廠房現已停產停業，封存產品，並已隔離 87 名密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%A0%E6%88%BF-8-%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%BB%A0%E6%88%BF%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A2-%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E5%B0%81%E5%AD%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF-8-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%25AD%2598%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Ywpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=d16774d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF-8-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%25AD%2598%2F&h=84502eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%A0%E6%88%BF-8-%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%BB%A0%E6%88%BF%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A2-%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E5%B0%81%E5%AD%98/</a>"},{"pid":"a4fb6cd3665b2fb36b1c9ae6d671ab371c54dc3f","tid":2073412,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"百事公司在深圳、廣州、福州、北京等多個地區都設有廠房，而香港百事可樂則由匯泉國際代理，其中有產品來自中國，暫未知爆發疫情的北京大興廠房會否有產品供應至本港。本網正就事件向匯泉國際查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc5142e0db4e74506623df9c556a4cc88a8e9a0","tid":2073412,"uid":53695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGzyTe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGzyTe0.jpg&h=6b9a01f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n纓紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}